197
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:58,640
But when I started to do hair, the people, they didn't like that too well because they

198
00:12:58,640 --> 00:13:05,200
knew the white people had told them that don't fool around with the Halloween because

199
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:11,880
bad thing was going on and they home getting people's register to vote and y'all don't need

200
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:17,240
