235
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,240
He didn't give up.

236
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:44,000
He just still was fighting for the rights of getting people's rage and vote.

237
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:49,680
And this night, but I knew that we was going to die just felt that we was going to be

